51:49.565 --> 51:53.236
It'd be awfully nice
to have a place to sit and eat!

51:53.402 --> 51:55.863
- Later!
♪ ..walk the plank

51:56.030 --> 51:59.325
♪ Plank, plank, plank, plank,
plank, plank, plank... ♪

51:59.492 --> 52:01.994
- Now.
- ♪ Here we come

52:02.161 --> 52:04.539
- ♪ Here we come... ♪
- Now! Now!

52:04.705 --> 52:07.291
You are so mean!

52:07.458 --> 52:10.128
- I am not your servant!
- No!

52:10.294 --> 52:12.713
Goddamnit!
I'm the servant!

52:12.880 --> 52:14.966
All I do is cook for you
and clean,

52:15.133 --> 52:18.427
and I drive you around and take care of
your every goddamn need!

52:18.594 --> 52:20.763
You treat me
like a goddamn maid!

52:20.930 --> 52:25.643
I got to get out of here!
Jock, go back. Go back!

52:27.687 --> 52:30.690
- We don't have a babysitter.
- You don't need a babysitter.

52:30.857 --> 52:33.609
But it's night-time.
We get scared. Faithie gets scared.

52:33.776 --> 52:36.362
Then you need to toughen up.
What is there to be scared of?

52:36.529 --> 52:38.531
- Wolves? Vampires?
- Rapists!

52:38.698 --> 52:41.576
Rapists? If a rapist knocks,
don't let him in!

52:41.742 --> 52:44.453
But what if they force their way in?
That's what rapists do!

52:44.620 --> 52:48.416
You kick them in the balls! Oh!
I need to get out of here!

52:48.583 --> 52:51.627
I can't take it anymore!
I need to go be with adults!

52:51.794 --> 52:54.589
Not a bunch
of bratty, bossy brats!

52:54.755 --> 52:56.924
Unhand my foot!

53:13.566 --> 53:15.234
Oh!

53:34.629 --> 53:37.798
Oh. Hi, Cam. Going up?

53:40.051 --> 53:41.594
I guess so.

53:45.723 --> 53:47.767
- You need help folding those?
- You know...

53:47.934 --> 53:50.686
Actually, I forgot something
in the laundry room.

54:16.045 --> 54:18.256
See, girls?
The chain's worthless.

54:18.422 --> 54:21.592
All it does is provide
a false sense of security.

54:21.759 --> 54:25.263
And that's the last thing you girls need.
Sorry I scared you.

54:25.429 --> 54:28.724
We'll be braver, Daddy.
Next time, I promise we'll be braver.

54:33.312 --> 54:35.940
Put yourselves to bed.
I've got a mess to clean up.

54:39.610 --> 54:41.821
That lock was bullshit.

56:24.882 --> 56:27.218
- What happened to the Valiant?
- I didn't I tell you?

56:27.385 --> 56:30.179
- It caught on fire.
- Oh.

56:50.783 --> 56:52.543
- I'm depressed.
- Of course you are.

56:52.618 --> 56:54.995
Your dog ran away,
your family gives you

56:55.162 --> 56:57.498
just barely enough money to live off,
and you annoy people.

56:57.665 --> 56:59.375
You're leaving out
my haemorrhoids.

56:59.542 --> 57:01.210
Where are you going?

57:01.377 --> 57:02.837
I'm meeting
Kim, Ali and Thurgood.

57:03.003 --> 57:04.380
- Can I come?
- I guess.

57:04.547 --> 57:05.548
Can I come?

57:05.714 --> 57:07.091
- No!
- God!

57:07.258 --> 57:08.843
We are hanging out
with our friends!

57:09.009 --> 57:10.689
Why don't you ever
bring your friends here?

57:10.761 --> 57:13.055
- To this shithole?
- Stop saying that!

57:13.222 --> 57:15.102
Daddy, you can't hang out with kids.
It's weird.

57:15.141 --> 57:17.643
We need to have our own life,
and you need to have yours.

57:17.810 --> 57:19.562
How am I supposed to
have my own life

57:19.728 --> 57:21.439
when you won't let me
do anything?

57:34.535 --> 57:37.079
Fine! We're hanging out
at the picnic tables.

57:41.500 --> 57:44.587
- The death card.
- Does that mean I'm gonna die?

57:44.753 --> 57:46.672
Well, we all die sometime.

57:46.839 --> 57:48.382
Let's start over.

57:49.717 --> 57:52.553
Oh. Any of you kids
have a light?

57:54.346 --> 57:56.182
Can we finish this
at your apartment?

57:56.348 --> 57:58.726
Our parents
just got a new sectional.

57:58.893 --> 58:01.061
- Never mind. Here's one.
- How about you?

58:01.228 --> 58:02.813
My brother
is studying for law school.

58:02.980 --> 58:04.982
You're all welcome
to come to our apartment.

58:06.358 --> 58:09.069
Cam, can we speak to you
for a minute?

58:10.571 --> 58:12.114
What? What?

58:14.408 --> 58:16.243
I am about to
lose my shit.

58:16.410 --> 58:18.913
We told you you could
come hang out with us.

58:19.079 --> 58:21.279
We did not say you could
invite people to the apartment.

58:21.415 --> 58:23.042
- But it could be fun.
- Not fun. Humiliating.

58:23.209 --> 58:25.336
- Do we need to spell it out?
- I can make tea.

